        "richtext_UcgeDQ": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Before the 2008 financial crisis, platinum faced a boom, with prices double than that of gold. Soon after, platinum price per 1 gram plummeted sharply. The same happened during the covid era. Prices dropped drastically during covid with intermittent recoveries that followed. The drop in platinum gram value was because of global lockdowns and disruptions in the auto sector which heavily relies on platinum in manufacturing of automobiles. Currently, 1 gram platinum price is recovering and is the best time to invest in platinum as it shows an upward potential while forecasting.  </p><p>You can now choose a dream platinum solitaire pendant or a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/tennis-bracelets\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Tennis Bracelets\">tennis bracelet</a> platinum or a platinum bangle at a much lesser price than gold. You can even buy a platinum bangle for men, which looks sharp, elegant and is versatile with every look!</p>"
          }
        },
